  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to dav1d</title>

    <para>
      The dav1d package contains an AV1 decoder.
    </para>

    &lfs130_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
